Our memberships:&#xd;
- According to law 281/98, MDC is member of CNCU (Italian National Committee of Consumers and Users). Link: http://www.sviluppoeconomico.gov.it/index.php/it/component/content/article?id=2003220&#xd;
- MDC is founder-member of Consumers’ Forum, association which aims to widespread ADR. Link: http://www.consumersforum.it/soci.html&#xd;
- MDC is member of Arci Servizio Civile Link: http://www.arciserviziocivile.it/ascnetwork/roma/socipartner/&#xd;
